'''威廉·阿瑟·劉易斯'''爵士（{{lang-en|Sir William Arthur Lewis}}，{{bd|1915年|1月23日|1991年|6月15日|catIdx=Lewis}}）是[[聖露西亞|聖露西亞]][[經濟學家|經濟學家]]，因為其於[[發展經濟學|發展經濟學]]上的貢獻而聞名。1979年，與[[西奥多·舒尔茨|西奥多·舒尔茨]]一同獲得[[諾貝爾經濟學獎|諾貝爾經濟學獎]]<ref name=nobel>[http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/laureates/1979/ "The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel 1979"] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HXOH4KJA?url=http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economic-sciences/laureates/1979/ |date=20130621085209 |dateformat=iso }}, Nobel in Economics, 1979, Accessed 5 Jan 2011{{en}}</ref>，第一位拿到[[諾貝爾獎|諾貝爾獎]]非和平獎項的[[黑人|黑人]]，迄今唯一一位拿到諾貝爾科學研究獎項的黑人。

== 刘易斯拐点 ==
[[刘易斯拐点|刘易斯拐点]]（Lewis Turning Point，又译“路易斯拐点”）<ref>Lewis, W. Arthur (1954). "Economic Development with Unlimited Supplies of Labor," ''Manchester School of Economic and Social Studies,'' Vol. 22, pp. 139–91 {{en}}</ref><ref name=Leeson>[[Phil_Leeson|Leeson, P. F.]] and Nixson, F. I. (2004)" Development economics in the Department of Economics at the University of Manchester", ''Journal of Economic Studies,'' Glasgow, Vol. 31, Iss. 1; p. 6 {{en}}</ref>由刘易斯在1968年提出，形容农村廉价劳动力被经济增长全部吸纳后，工资会显著上升。路易斯用这套理论显示工业化与城市化进程是解决农村贫困问题的最佳途经。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601068&sid=aZGJ0mc_Dm5o | work=Bloomberg | title=China Reaches Turning Point as Inflation Overtakes Labor | date=June 11, 2010 |  language=en}}</ref><ref>[http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/20100715-China-Cheap-Labor-End-at-Lewis-Turning-Point-98550389.html “路易斯拐点”- 中国廉价劳力提前终结？] {{Wayback|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/20100715-China-Cheap-Labor-End-at-Lewis-Turning-Point-98550389.html |date=20101114125334 }}{{zh-cn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mag.nownews.com/article.php?mag=1-31-4268 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809075250/http://mag.nownews.com/article.php?mag=1-31-4268 |archivedate=2011-08-09 }}{{zh-tw}}</ref>

